OL,3,CFurther travel disruption expected as
OL,4,CTube drivers stage week's second strike
OL,6,FTransport for London (TfL) continued
OL,7,Fto advise people to check before they
OL,8,Ftravel for the rest of the week.
OL,10,FThe union is in dispute with London
OL,11,FUnderground over changes to the
OL,12,Fworking week, including shift patterns.
OL,14,FMore 24-hour strikes are planned in
OL,15,FMay and June unless the row is
OL,16,Fresolved.
OL,18,FPicket lines will be mounted outside
OL,19,FTube stations from noon on Thursday.
